{"tid":2374524,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"買波證券化","createTime":"2021-01-21T09:43:34.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-22T13:15:58.000Z","uid":89046,"like":36,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"c1b1d8c690cac0c62349a68913a7b89b8e6681d0","tid":2374524,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:43:34.000Z","msg":"馬會應該發行球會認購證<br />\n例如 &lsquo;利記英超認購證 Liverpool EPL Call&rsquo;<br />\n每年英超季初開始發行 季尾結算<br />\n行使條款係球隊聯賽得分季尾要至少有X分<br />\n如果冇就價外<br />\n如果有 結算日個payoff就係（最終聯賽績分 - X）再乘以槓桿倍數<br />\n<br />\n隻輪係自由買賣<br />\n因此球隊表現及相關新聞對於輪價有關鍵影響 如果係短線睇好嘅話都可以短炒<br />\n<br />\n球隊死忠可以於季初long call揸到尾<br />\n睇死利記嘅可以選擇short call賺期權金 馬會又可以outsource個風險出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n更進一步可以玩埋動物  &lsquo;利記英超牛證&rsquo;<br />\n加入打靶條款 例如連輸3場即收回 等個買入成本平啲 同時又可以玩大啲波幅 如果利記前兩場都輸 想搏之後嗰場唔洗打靶就可以大量買入<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n發行球會輪證不但促進香港作為亞洲金融中心嘅地位<br />\n更為香港市民提供適切嘅風險管理工具 為國際投資者提供嶄新嘅資產選擇 更有助達致全民體育目標 實在係百利而無一害 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86818c89511c5c783618cc94ac3dd9330511e14d","tid":2374524,"uid":127342,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:48:03.000Z","msg":"外國莊一早有哂呢啲，邊隊幾多分，仲有分全季半季玩，季中仲可以cash out<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過馬會連即場讓球都唔敢開，你叫佢搞呢啲真係哂鳩氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"049a5e9875f277386de7200b5d31439b230c6964","tid":2374524,"uid":89046,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"86818c89511c5c783618cc94ac3dd9330511e14d","tid":2374524,"uid":127342,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T09:48:03.000Z","msg":"外國莊一早有哂呢啲，邊隊幾多分，仲有分全季半季玩，季中仲可以cash out<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過馬會連即場讓球都唔敢開，你叫佢搞呢啲真係哂鳩氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T10:05:14.000Z","msg":"馬會垃圾就有目共睹架啦<br />\n我嘅想法係要比班bookies更進一步<br />\n將所謂嘅賭博變為可以喺exchange trade嘅asset<br />\n<br />\n有咩理由你跟ibank買輪就係投資 係風險管理 <br />\n跟馬會買波就係賭<br />\n<br />\n我宜家買一個financial derivative<br />\n個underlying就係球會聯賽嘅表現<br />\n唔算係賭 而係投資 係風險管理<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0318f23a9a3d85645b941e5f1fcc1e91d612094","tid":2374524,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T15:23:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9b4ba59aeb37c4fb2b0d5b95d35b087ca301d0f","tid":2374524,"uid":28415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T15:36:24.000Z","msg":"太高質無人識討論<br />\n你開係波台都可能有人屌你咁姐係開唔開賭波谷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18365897448d0449f73a10c33bd524f5e22cc19d","tid":2374524,"uid":89046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e9b4ba59aeb37c4fb2b0d5b95d35b087ca301d0f","tid":2374524,"uid":28415,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T15:36:24.000Z","msg":"太高質無人識討論<br />\n你開係波台都可能有人屌你咁姐係開唔開賭波谷<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T17:22:46.000Z","msg":"連財經台都唔講得衍生產品<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46f1b75b0da653bfa70b72fd67d3b6f685f89f0","tid":2374524,"uid":2590,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T17:42:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"471434ef78014459fcd9467864241ae6ef3f84d1","tid":2374524,"uid":227275,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T18:07:34.000Z","msg":"d賭撚賭到傻撚左<br />\n正正經經買正股算撚數喇"},{"pid":"7e45ee818a200f7170895ebb1d82d4cc2eb52cf0","tid":2374524,"uid":173852,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T23:27:17.000Z","msg":"係咪姐係Betfair?"},{"pid":"e9180d62a511e2138400ce0ca8e5d3dedc0d37c1","tid":2374524,"uid":29041,"like":2,"dislike":